* Sub String Operation

SUBSTR :- ( STR, pos, num)

  Step 1: [ Initialization ]
          i <- 0
          j <- 0   
          pos
          num
          substr = Null
  Step 2: [ input the value ]
          Read (str, pos, num)

  Step 3: [ Copy the string Str to subject string]
          i = pos
          while(str[i] != 0 && num > 0) repeat
              substr[j] = str[i]
              i = i + 1
              j = j + 1
              num = num - 1
  Step 4: [print sub string]
          Print("substr")

  Step 5: [ Finished ] & Exit
